{"tid":439007,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[升級路線] 主力玩大光圈定焦, 留係M43定轉會Fuji?","createTime":"2017-10-17T12:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T15:11:24.000Z","uid":46749,"like":18,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"11d70d833abb31b4bf5c2bffad0d7b56c1317480","tid":439007,"uid":46749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T12:25:38.000Z","msg":"本身玩左M43 4-5年, 主要貪細部同輕, 而家仲用緊GX7 + 12/2.0 或 20/1.7 或 45/1.8 (旅行多數前兩支, 影女友個陣換45)<br />\n但係發覺夜晚影野有時雜訊都多, 我已經開哂防震同盡量ISO 800樓下<br />\n近年發覺Fuji好似多人用, 見到D人都係玩定焦, 心郁郁想轉會<br />\n但又覺得EM-1 mark 2好正<br />\n用慣M43唔想用番單反, 太重而且嚇親路人<br />\n<br />\n我主要都係旅行用, 影街頭 (有時會深夜出街影), 風景, 女友, 家庭相, 近乎不拍片<br />\nD相主要都係直出JPG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉會Fuji<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續玩M43啦你"},{"pid":"b37752ae4a0d462e3b71bef42ede21e7467041de","tid":439007,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"如果你講大光圈fuju一定俾M43大啦"},{"pid":"02c0df677bd6df2934d7dc80ebb216b0efe3402e","tid":439007,"uid":46749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你講大光圈fuju一定俾M43大啦</blockquote><br />\n個支16/1.4 同 56/1.2 D相真係睇到扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70701fb93201115900571014be8e441470ba745","tid":439007,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:32:12.000Z","msg":"如果em1mk2 價錢ok<br />\n咁考唔考慮rx1r2"},{"pid":"960bbb6737e63ddc91459283dc6b53e0fc16d90a","tid":439007,"uid":14840,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"係多人用啊<br />\n不過都多人放呢<br />\n傻仔先買富士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e5a18165f2eab55f53cb82c32f9c816985e641","tid":439007,"uid":53983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2